  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether patients drinking their bowel preparation
      solution with a straw will have improved tolerability for ingestion of their bowel
      preparation solution and achieve a higher bowel preparation quality score than patients
      drinking their bowel preparation solution without a straw.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
